Package: BEPSDashboard
Title: BEPS Advanced Data Visualization Dashboard
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-04-07
Author: GitHub Copilot
Maintainer: GitHub Copilot <copilot@github.com>
Description: Interactive R Shiny dashboard for analyzing the British Election Panel 
    Study (BEPS) 2001 dataset. Features include vote distribution analysis, age-based 
    voting trends, economic perception analysis, leader ratings, and comprehensive 
    data visualization. Built for VIT Course CSI 3005 - Advanced Data Visualization 
    Techniques. Includes 6 interactive tabs, 13+ visualizations, global filters, KPI 
    cards, and automated insight generation.
